{
  "texts": [
    "Token frequency distribution convert the corpus to tokens and extract a table of unique tokens along with their frequency of occurrence.",
    "Hence, the table represents the TFD needed to build the vocabulary.",
    "Vocabulary initialization build a base vocabulary using 256 bytes from the 8-bit Unicode Transformation Format (UTF-8 {XE \"UTF-8:unicode transformation format (8-bit)\"}).",
    "The first 128 symbols of UTF-8 correspond to the standard English ASCII characters.",
    "UTF-8 is the dominant encoding on the internet, accounting for approximately 98% of all web pages (W3Techs 2023)."
  ]
}